{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yewstack/yew/issues/3043","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yewstack/yew","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yewstack/yew/issues/3043/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yewstack/yew/issues/3043/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yewstack/yew/issues/3043/events","html_url":"https://github.com/yewstack/yew/issues/3043","id":1499889935,"node_id":"I_kwDOBtKdYc5ZZoEP","number":3043,"title":"Uncaught RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded","user":{"login":"maurerdietmar","id":16542869,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2NTQyODY5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16542869?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar","html_url":"https://github.com/maurerdietmar","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maurerdietmar/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":792840709,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw3OTI4NDA3MDk=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yewstack/yew/labels/bug","name":"bug","color":"75ad20","default":true,"description":""}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":4,"created_at":"2022-12-16T09:41:34Z","updated_at":"2023-01-09T14:08:11Z","closed_at":"2023-01-09T14:08:11Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"We still get this bug:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/yewstack/yew/issues/1449\r\nhttps://github.com/yewstack/yew/issues/1635\r\n\r\nI think the implemention of  PartialEq for NodeRef is terribly wrong:\r\n\r\n```\r\nimpl PartialEq for NodeRef {\r\n    fn eq(&self, other: &Self) -> bool {\r\n        self.0.as_ptr() == other.0.as_ptr() || Some(self) == other.0.borrow().link.as_ref()\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nBecause \"Some(self) == other.0.borrow().link.as_ref()\" call  PartialEq recursively?!\r\n\r\nAside from  that, the additional check seems to be unnecessary, because it can never trigger.\r\n\r\n```\r\n  pub(crate) fn link(&self, node_ref: Self) {\r\n            // Avoid circular references\r\n            debug_assert!(\r\n                self != &node_ref,\r\n                \"no circular references allowed! Report this as a bug in yew\"\r\n            );\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe following patch solves the problem  for me:\r\n\r\n```\r\n diff --git a/packages/yew/src/html/mod.rs b/packages/yew/src/html/mod.rs\r\nindex 28fa84af..f840a526 100644\r\n--- a/packages/yew/src/html/mod.rs\r\n+++ b/packages/yew/src/html/mod.rs\r\n@@ -92,7 +92,7 @@ pub struct NodeRef(Rc<RefCell<NodeRefInner>>);\r\n \r\n impl PartialEq for NodeRef {\r\n     fn eq(&self, other: &Self) -> bool {\r\n-        self.0.as_ptr() == other.0.as_ptr() || Some(self) == other.0.borrow().link.as_ref()\r\n+        self.0.as_ptr() == other.0.as_ptr()\r\n     }\r\n }\r\n \r\n\r\n```","closed_by":{"login":"WorldSEnder","id":6527051,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY1MjcwNTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6527051?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/WorldSEnder","html_url":"https://github.com/WorldSEnder","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WorldSEnder/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.